=head1 DESCRIPTION

Defines the resources that the Firewall Manager administrator can
manage. For more information about administrative scope, see Managing
Firewall Manager administrators
(https://docs.aws.amazon.com/waf/latest/developerguide/fms-administrators.html)
in the I<Firewall Manager Developer Guide>.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 AccountScope => L<Paws::FMS::AccountScope>

Defines the accounts that the specified Firewall Manager administrator
can apply policies to.


=head2 OrganizationalUnitScope => L<Paws::FMS::OrganizationalUnitScope>

Defines the Organizations organizational units that the specified
Firewall Manager administrator can apply policies to. For more
information about OUs in Organizations, see Managing organizational
units (OUs)
(https://docs.aws.amazon.com/organizations/latest/userguide/orgs_manage_ous.html)
in the I<Organizations User Guide>.


=head2 PolicyTypeScope => L<Paws::FMS::PolicyTypeScope>

Defines the Firewall Manager policy types that the specified Firewall
Manager administrator can create and manage.


=head2 RegionScope => L<Paws::FMS::RegionScope>

Defines the Amazon Web Services Regions that the specified Firewall
Manager administrator can perform actions in.



